{"ts":"2026-06-17T04:00:00+00:00","source":"evolve-strategy","mode":"hypothesis","strategy":"vol_target_momentum","baseline":"momentum_12_1","universe":"broad_pit","params":{"top_n":20,"target_vol":0.3,"vol_window":20,"regime_ma":200,"rebalance":"monthly","universe_size":200,"sizing":"risk_based","asof":"2017-01-01","split":"2022-06-30"},"splits":[{"name":"IS","start":"2017-01-01","end":"2022-06-30","sharpe":0.178},{"name":"OOS","start":"2022-07-01","end":"2026-06-16","sharpe":0.475}],"decay":-0.297,"fitness":0.42,"gate":"satellite","hypothesis":"Does the de-biased overlay edge hold on the recovery split too (split-robust), or give up upside as on the look-ahead universe?","notes":"FIRST SATELLITE PROMOTION. Full de-biased 2-split: overlay beats baseline on BOTH splits -- crash +0.51 vs -0.216, recovery +0.475 vs +0.422. Mean OOS +0.49 vs baseline +0.10, both positive, negative decay (OOS>IS). OPPOSITE of the look-ahead universe (iter-9: overlay LOST recovery +0.34 vs +0.93) -- the look-ahead high-flyers had inflated the baseline recovery and HID the overlay edge. Survivorship correction revealed a true positive. GATE=SATELLITE (beats baseline all splits, low decay, survives de-biasing). NOT CORE: mean 0.49 < SPY buy-hold 0.53, does not beat buy-hold. CAVEATS: deflated-Sharpe check only marginal (both splits ~0.48-0.51 vs ~0.4 noise band for ~100 trials) -- a formal DSR is the next rigor step; coverage survivorship (delisted absent) remains.","run_id":"2026-06-17T04:00:00+00:00-vol_target_momentum-b299"}
